Treasury Policies

The engine can validate treasury rules such as:

Maximum asset allocation
Minimum stablecoin reserves
Maximum protocol exposure
Chain diversification requirements
Minimum liquidity buffer
Approved counterparties only

Example policy:

{
  "max_single_asset": 40,
  "min_stablecoin": 20,
  "max_protocol_exposure": 25
}
